@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Test GET login page
GET {{baseUrl}}/login

### Test POST register (succès)
POST {{baseUrl}}/register
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=testuser1&email=tests@example.com&password=Password123&verify_password=Password123

### Test POST register (erreur - mots de passe ne correspondent pas)
POST {{baseUrl}}/register
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=testuser2&email=test2@example.com&password=Password123&verify_password=DifferentPassword

### Test POST login (succès)
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=testuser&password=Password123

### Test POST login (erreur - utilisateur inexistant)
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=nonexistent&password=Password123

### Test POST login (erreur - mauvais mot de passe)
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=testuser&password=WrongPassword

### Test GET logout
GET {{baseUrl}}/logout


